==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Xanthian
<hw>Xan"thi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
<etsep>Xanthus</etsep>, an ancient town on Asia Minor; -- applied
especially to certain marbles found near that place, and now in the
British Museum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Xanthic</ent>⟦br⟧
